 Carnatic Music Association, Atlanta jointly with Hindu Temple of
 Atlanta, announces the following programs:
 
 March 7, Saturday Great Composer's day celebration - starting 8:30
 in the morning with singing of pancharatna kritis and ending at 6:30
 with singing of Utsava sampradhaya kritis.  Individuals interested
 in singing or playing instruments are invited to participate.
 

